{"tid":2305566,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"估吾到我竟然係輕鐵站會執到五十蚊","createTime":"2020-11-29T17:37:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-29T17:58:49.000Z","uid":184629,"like":7,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"93fd66ec44f9b546725c2cd8ee897ed2c86da715","tid":2305566,"uid":184629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T17:37:16.000Z","msg":"是咁的，有一晚我經過一個平時好小機會行過既輕鐵站，突然比我見到地上面有張綠色正方形嘅紙，我行近去再望兩眼 發現竟然係張五十蚊紙。<br />\n<br />\n果一下我簡直覺得自己就係天選之人，放係古代應該都同秦始皇同級。首先從機率上嚟講，係香港發行既紙幣數量上，五十蚊同一千蚊既稀有度係一樣，每十張紙幣只有一張係五十蚊。<br />\n<br />\n第二就係搭輕鐵一般只會用八達通，極少機會有人拎現金出嚟，更何況係輕鐵站呢個人來人往嘅地方，竟然會全部人都見唔呢一張綠色嘅五十蚊紙，係幾難得嘅事。<br />\n<br />\n就係咁，當我見到嘅時候，二話不說即刻拎起左同佢拍照留念...然後放番低係原位，希望有下一個幸運兒可以一齊分享呢份喜悅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[url][img]<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fWJfofj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfWJfofj.jpg&h=79d35924&s={SIZE}\" />[/img][/url]"},{"pid":"863555188866f9395cdcfacaea8bea17dd4b24ea","tid":2305566,"uid":149257,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T17:42:09.000Z","msg":"有錢都唔識執，善良師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3918bcf89d36c2042905728eea9a7174708ff60f","tid":2305566,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"863555188866f9395cdcfacaea8bea17dd4b24ea","tid":2305566,"uid":149257,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T17:42:09.000Z","msg":"有錢都唔識執，善良師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T17:45:13.000Z","msg":"樓主身家500億<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed792bdc6e797d1aa60fff327252def56fd0d320","tid":2305566,"uid":190187,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T17:58:49.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">吾你老母</span></span>"}]}